# Target goal position given as:
float64 x
float64 y
float64 theta

---
# Result to be rendered as:
bool success
float64 final_x
float64 final_y
float64 final_theta
string message

---
# Feedback to be continuously rendered as:
float64 current_x
float64 current_y
float64 current_theta
float64 distance_error
float64 heading_error
string phase